data.name: TxtHelp.Text
data.value: To work out your overall grade simply put in the number of Passes, Merits and Distinctions scored (max 18) using the arrow buttons. Once you have entered them all simply click the calculate grade button which will show your overall grade. Below is a table showing the grade system for the BTEC course. The application uses the data in this table to work out the overall grade. A grade for a unit is equally to a certain amount of points, when these points are totalled they can be used to work out the overall grade with this table.
